[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0851","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0851.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0583","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 域信任关系安全漏洞","description":"Windows NT 域间存在单向或双向信任关系配置安全隐患，远程攻击者可在无需认证且利用复杂度低的情况下，利用域间信任机制突破访问控制边界，从已控制的受信任域向目标域横向移动，通过传递身份验证请求获取目标域资源的未授权访问权限，实现跨域渗透。CVSS v2 评分 10.0，可导致目标系统机密性、完整性和可用性完全受损。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0583"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.710","remediation":"建议立即将 Windows NT 4.0 升级至受支持版本（Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本），启用 SID 筛选以防范信任提升攻击。仅在业务必要下建立域信任，并设置为单向而非双向信任，同时为每个信任配置隔离。对所有域控制器持续安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1284","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0583","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0583.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9r38-2pp7-328c/GHSA-9r38-2pp7-328c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86240/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d