dules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0846","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0846.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0580","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE 注册表键存在权限配置不当漏洞，该键存储操作系统核心安全与配置信息，但默认权限设置过于宽松，导致未授权用户可读取甚至修改其中的系统关键项。攻击者可利用不当权限访问或篡改 HKLM 下安全策略、服务配置等关键数据，造成敏感信息泄露、权限提升乃至系统完全受控。该漏洞影响全系 Windows NT 操作系统，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0580"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.357","remediation":"Windows NT 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本。如无法升级，需手动收紧注册表权限：运行 regedt32，展开 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE，右键选择「权限」，移除 Everyone 组的完全控制权，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 的读取权限，并应用强制 ACL 继承到所有子项。同时部署组策略限制本地注册表远程访问。作为临时缓解，限制对受影响主机的网络访问并启用注册表审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0580","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0580.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0580","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0580.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86248/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0846.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0845","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0845.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0579","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表审核策略日志记录缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的注册表审计策略存在缺陷，系统未对非关键注册表键的访问事件记录成功或失败的审计日志。该漏洞导致对这些注册表键值的修改、创建或删除操作无法被安全日志捕获，使得管理员无法通过审计日志追踪对非关键注册表项的未授权更改。攻击者可能利用此审计缺失，在未留下可追溯痕迹的情况下修改系统配置或注册表项，降低系统的审计完整性和安全可见性，间接增加了后续攻击活动的隐匿性和成功概率。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0579"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.243","remediation":"建议安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新。通过域安全策略或本地安全策略启用「审计对象访问」，覆盖所有注册表项；针对非关键注册表项手动配置审核条目，如使用注册表编辑器为关键项添加 SYSTEM 审计访问。无法立即修复时部署第三方注册表监控工具（如 Sysinternals Regmon）补充审计缺失。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/228","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0579","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0579.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86238/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a38c45d0-f252-4969-8539-5c22f5a47cc8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0845.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0844","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0844.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0578","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表审核策略日志遗漏漏洞","description":"Windows NT 注册表审核策略存在缺陷，系统未能对安全关键注册表键的访问和修改操作记录成功或失败事件日志。本地攻击者可通过修改注册表敏感项绕过安全审计，实施权限提升或系统配置篡改等攻击，且相关操作不会被系统日志记录。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0578"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.117","remediation":"通过注册表编辑器 (regedt32.exe) 对安全关键注册表项（如 HKLM\\SAM、HKLM\\SECURITY、HKLM\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion）启用审核，设置 \"审核策略\" 中的 \"审核对象访问\" 为 \"成功和失败\"。同时使用 Windows NT 资源包中的 auditpol.exe 工具确认审核策略已生效。Windows NT 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2008/2012/2019/2022 等受支持版本以获得完整安全审计能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/228","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0578.json","https://github.