a modern Windows server version\n- Configure file audit policies properly\n- Provide specific steps and mitigation measures分析：CVE-1999-0577涉及Windows NT系统的文件审计策略未记录非关键文件/目录的成功/失败事件。根据漏洞描述，需要修复Windows NT的日志审计功能。\n\n<value>升级到Windows Server 2003 SP1或更高版本，使用本地安全策略配置“拒绝访问检查”和“成功/失败审计”策略，对于旧系统可通过修改注册表项[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa]下的Audit基址来启用审计日志记录，如无法立即升级，建议通过组策略强制启用文件审计策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0577.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p3j3-4263-vqh3/GHSA-p3j3-4263-vqh3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0843.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0836","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0836.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0571","title":"ZyXEL Prestige Router 管理接口未授权访问漏洞","description":"ZyXEL Prestige 路由器管理接口存在访问控制缺陷，其 Web 或 Telnet 等配置服务默认允许来自任意主机的连接，未经授权的远程攻击者可直接访问管理控制台进行配置修改、信息窃取或权限提升。该漏洞影响多个 ZyXEL Prestige 系列路由器型号，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商建议通过限制管理接口访问来源 IP 或禁用远程管理功能进行缓解。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0571"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.527","remediation":"登录路由器管理界面，在「远程管理」(Remote Management) 中将「Secured Client IP」设为仅信任的管理员地址，切勿设为 0.0.0.0；同时在防火墙 ACL 中限制仅允许指定管理 IP 访问 Web(80/443) 和 Telnet(23) 端口。如无需 WAN 侧管理，彻底关闭 WAN 远程管理功能，仅保留 LAN 侧访问；若设备固件版本过旧，建议升级至最新固件或更换支持 SSH/HTTPS 安全管理的现代设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0571","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0571","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0571.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0571.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/zyxel_pwd.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c7jg-hmf3-2v5x/GHSA-c7jg-hmf3-2v5x.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/zyxel_http_pwd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/ba2871b745cd47cb93c3c9bf946eced10fd29f5c/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0571.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0836.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0835","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0835.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0570","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 密码筛选器未启用弱密码策略漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统未启用密码筛选工具（如 PASSFILT.DLL），导致密码复杂度策略无法正常执行，用户可设置空密码或弱密码。远程攻击者可通过暴力破解弱密码获得系统未授权访问权限，进而完全控制受影响的 Windows NT 系统。该漏洞影响所有未启用密码筛选功能的 Windows NT 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0570"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.403","remediation":"在注册表 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa 中新建 Notification Packages 多字符串值，添加 PASSFILT 启用密码筛选器；通过本地安全策略（secpol.msc）开启密码必须符合复杂性要求，设置密码长度最小值≥8 位、密码最长使用期限≤90 天，确保 PASSFilt.dll 存在于 %SystemRoot%\\System32 目录中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0570","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0570","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0570.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9jjm-6ch3-q532/GHSA-9jjm-6ch3-q532.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0570.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6462f8a3-83c0-4a77-ad26-29b452334a82.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0835.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0834","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0834.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0569","title":"Web 服务器目录自动索引信息泄露漏洞","description":"WWW 目录启用了自动索引（目录浏览）功能，当目录中不存在 index.html 等默认索引文件时，远程攻击者通过浏览器直接访问该目录即可获取目录内所有文件的完整列表，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响大量未正确配置的 Web 服务器（包括 Apache、Nginx、IIS 等），攻击者无需任何身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。修复方式为关闭目录自动索引功能或在目录中添加默认索引文件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0569"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.290","remediation":"在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx/IIS）配置中禁用目录自动索引功能。Apache 需将 `Options Indexes` 改为 `Options -Indexes`；Nginx 设置 `autoindex off`；IIS 取消「目录浏览」权限。同时确保每个目录存在默认首页文件（如 index.html）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0569","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0569.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0569","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0569.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0569.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86062/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/C/cgibin_browsable.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0834.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0831","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0831.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0568","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.admind 不安全配置漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统中的 rpc.admind 服务默认未以安全模式运行，导致其在处理远程管理请求时缺乏有效的身份认证与访问控制机制。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络直接连接该服务并发送管理指令，从而以高权限在目标系统上执行任意命令、修改系统配置或获取敏感信息。该漏洞影响运行 Solaris 的主机，攻击条件较低，仅需能够访问目标开放的 rpc.admind 服务端口即可利用，CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。管理员应将 rpc.admind 配置为安全模式运行并限制相关端口的网络访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0568"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.160","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 针对 Solstice AdminSuite 的安全补丁（如补丁 ID 106235-xx 等对应版本），或升级至受支持的 Solaris 版本。如无需远程管理功能，执行以下操作禁用该服务：编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释掉 rpc.admind 相关行后重启 inetd，或在 SMF 环境下执行 svcadm disable svc:/network/rpc/admind:default。同时，在防火墙层面限制对 TCP 端口 2325 的入站访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0568","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0568","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0568.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5pmv-f82w-3v96/GHSA-5pmv-f82w-3v96.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0568.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0831.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0828","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0828.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0565","title":"Sendmail 别名管道命令执行漏洞","description":"Sendmail 的别名（alias）功能允许将电子邮件内容通过管道（pipe）传递给指定程序执行，远程攻击者可利用此机制发送特制邮件触发目标系统执行任意命令，从而导致远程代码执行。该漏洞影响广泛使用的 Sendmail 邮件服务器软件，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级严重（CVSS 10.0），可导致服务器完全受控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0565"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.933","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本，启用 smrsh（SendMail Restricted SHell）限制别名可调用的程序列表，仅允许白名单内的安全程序（如 mail、vacation）。同时在 /etc/mail/aliases 中移除或审查所有调用外部程序的管道别名，避免将未经消毒的输入传递给管道命令。如无法升级，可在 mc 配置中加入 FEATURE(smrsh) 并设置 smrsh 可执行路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0565","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0565.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0565","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0565.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0565.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86048/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0828.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0822","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0822.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0561","title":"Microsoft IIS 服务器端包含远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 服务器存在服务器端包含（SSI）功能安全缺陷，默认启用了 #exec 指令执行权限。远程攻击者可通过上传包含恶意 #exec 指令的 .shtml/.stm 文件至可写目录，触发目标服务器执行任意系统命令，导致完全控制服务器。该漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。微软官方已发布安全公告并建议禁用 SSI #exec 功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0561"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.580","remediation":"建议立即升级至 IIS 4.0 及以上版本并安装微软发布的安全补丁（如 MS99-023）。配置层面：在 IIS 管理器中禁用 SSI 的 #exec 指令，或完全关闭服务器端包含 (SSI) 功能。临时缓解：在防火墙层面限制对 Web 服务器的非必要访问，并监控异常 SSI 请求日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0561","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0561.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0561","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0561.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0561.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86059/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0822.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0822.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0821","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0821.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0560","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 系统文件权限漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中关键系统文件或目录权限设置不当，导致低权限用户或本地攻击者可能读取、修改或删除系统关键文件，从而造成信息泄露、权限提升或系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，攻击者只需拥有本地访问权限即可利用，无需特殊条件。攻击者可利用不当权限覆盖系统文件或获取敏感信息，严重威胁系统安全性。微软已在后续安全更新中修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0560"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.460","remediation":"使用 Windows NT 资源工具包中的 cacls 或 xcacls 工具，将系统关键目录（如 %SystemRoot%、%SystemRoot%\\System32）的权限设置为 Administrators 和 SYSTEM 完全控制，Users 仅读取和执行。对于已停止支持的 Windows NT 4.0，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本以持续获取安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0560","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0560","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0560.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mwpg-5ghf-jf2p/GHSA-mwpg-5ghf-jf2p.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0560.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0821.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0820","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0820.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0559","title":"Unix 系统关键文件或目录权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Unix/Linux 系统中关键文件或目录权限设置不当的安全问题。当 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow 等系统关键文件或目录权限过于宽松（如全局可写）时，本地攻击者可利用不安全的权限配置读取敏感信息、修改系统文件或植入恶意代码，从而实现权限提升或完全控制系统。该漏洞源于未遵循最小权限原则进行配置，影响所有 Unix/Linux 衍生系统，攻击者只需本地访问权限即可利用，无需认证，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0559"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.350","remediation":"立即检查并修复系统关键文件和目录的权限：使用 `chmod 644 /etc/passwd /etc/group` 和 `chmod 600 /etc/shadow /etc/gshadow` 恢复标准权限。对 `/bin`、`/sbin`、`/usr/bin` 等目录使用 `chmod 755`。建议定期运行 `rpm -Va`（RPM 系）或 `debsums`（Debian 系）审计文件权限异常。同时排查是否存在被提权的后门账户或 SUID 异常文件（`find / -perm -4000`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0559","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0559.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0559","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0559.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0559.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86045/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0820.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0818","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0818.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0556","title":"Unix 系统账户 UID 重复安全漏洞","description":"Unix/Linux 系统中用户权限控制基于 UID（用户 ID）而非用户名进行判断，当两个或多个系统账户被错误配置为相同的 UID 时，这些账户将共享完全相同的文件访问权限和资源所有权。此问题属于系统管理配置缺陷，攻击者可以利用共享 UID 的其他账户访问本不应授权的文件或资源，导致信息泄露或权限提升。该漏洞影响各类 Unix 发行版，需通过审计并修正账户 UID 配置进行修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0556"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:38.230","remediation":"使用 `awk -F: '{print $3}' /etc/passwd | sort | uniq -d` 检查重复 UID，对冲突账户执行 `usermod -u 新UID 用户名` 分配唯一 UID，并用 `find / -uid 旧UID -exec chown -h 新UID {} +` 更新文件属主。同时建立用户创建流程确保自动分配不重复 UID。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/876","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0556","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0556.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-573h-p65m-cffp/GHSA-573h-p65m-cffp.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0556.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8053b2ad-2b59-4ec8-9ecf-84ad76b3b9bc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0818.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0818.toml"}]